

   MVC ( Model View Controller ) arch-pattern
   ---------------------------------------------
   
   
   Model
   --------
   
   	--> data
   	
   	
   View
   ----------
   
    -> User Interface
    
    
   Controller
   -----------  	
   
    --> provides data & behav to View
    
    
   ---------------------------------------------------
   
   
   adv MVC
   -----------
   
   
    --> easy to maintain
    --> easy to test
    --> easy to extend
    --> well-known and proven pattern
    
   
  -------------------------------------------------------
  
  
  How to implement this pattern in java based web-appln ?
  
  
  
  refer : http://images.techhive.com/images/idge/imported/article/jvw/1999/12/model2_sml-100158072-orig.gif
  
  
  
  -----------------------------------------------------------
  
  
  
  
  case-study : PM ( Product Management )
  
  
   Model:
   ------
   
   	-> Product
   	
   	Layer(s)
   	
   	a. Service Layer  
   	b. Data Layer
   	
   View
   --------
   
    -> Home View ( .html )
    -> PM View 	 ( .jsp  )
    
  
  Controller ( Web layer )
  --------------------------
  
  	-> ProductController ( servlet )
  	
  	   
  --------------------------------------------------------------
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
    
   
   
    